    <body>
        <p>Individual <code class="language-text">globalSecondaryIndex</code> objects have the following nested attributes:</p>
        <MadCap:snippetBlock src="change-type-local-global-secondary-index-shared-attributes.flsnp" />
        <ul>
            <li><code class="language-text">provisionedThroughput</code>&#160;<b>(optional)</b>: specifies the provisioned throughput settings for the index.<ul><li><code class="language-text">readCapacityUnits</code>&#160;<b>(required)</b>: the maximum number of reads per second before throttling.</li><li><code class="language-text">writeCapacityUnits</code>&#160;<b>(required)</b>: the maximum number of writes per second before throttling.</li></ul></li>
        </ul>
    </body>
</html>